<item>
 <title>E se desligarem a internet?</title>
 <link>http://mutgamb.org/blog/E-se-desligarem-internet</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Essa foi uma das perguntas que Felipe Fonseca incluiu em sua apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da &lt;a href=&quot;http://desvio.cc/blog/mobilefest-09&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;ZASF, em novembro de 2009, no MIS, durante o Mobile Fest, em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo-SP&lt;/a&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ontem, os 84 blocos de endere&amp;ccedil;os IP atribu&amp;iacute;dos a S&amp;iacute;ria foram &amp;quot;desligados&amp;quot;. Ou seja, nenhuma infoma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entra, nenhuma informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o sai, em um pa&amp;iacute;s do Oriente M&amp;eacute;dio que vive uma guerra civil....&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://allthingsd.com/files/2012/11/A84F1v7CAAAl3LU-640x480.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 420px; height: 315px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Adriano Belis&amp;aacute;rio compartilhou tr&amp;ecirc;s links que relataram essa informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* &lt;a href=&quot;http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57556156-93/blackout-syria-vanishes-from-internet/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;CNET News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* &lt;a href=&quot;http://allthingsd.com/20121129/syria-has-disappeared-from-the-internet/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;All Things&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20546302&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt; BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
